"'''Callista'''" is a category found on [[StarWars.com]] that collectively refers to the [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] adult-fiction novels [[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']] ([[1995]]), [[Darksaber (novel)|''Darksaber'']] (1995), and ''[[Planet of Twilight]]'' ([[1997]]). The name is derived from the character [[Callista Ming]], who plays a significant role in the three novels.

